'''''American Garage''''' is the second [[album]] by the [[Pat Metheny Group]], released in 1980.

==Track listing==
All tracks were composed by Pat Metheny & Lyle Mays:

# "(Cross the) Heartland" <U+2013> 6:55
# "Airstream" <U+2013> 6:20
# "The Search" <U+2013> 4:54
# "American Garage" <U+2013> 4:13
# "The Epic" <U+2013> 12:59

==Personnel==
* [[Pat Metheny]] - [[Guitar]], 12 String Guitar, [[Bass Guitar]]
* [[Lyle Mays]] - [[Piano]], [[keyboard instrument|keyboards]], [[Organ (music)|Organ]], [[Oberheim]], [[Autoharp]]
* [[Mark Egan]] - [[Bass Guitar]]
* [[Dan Gottlieb]] - [[Drum kit|drums]]

